Accessing context in a step
```ts
scenario("Context Example")
  .step("Use context", (ctx) => {
    console.log(`Running: ${ctx.name}`);
    console.log(`Tags: ${ctx.options.tags.join(", ")}`);
    console.log(`Previous results: ${ctx.results.length}`);
  })
  .build();
```

